  • Classes in ktt.lib.httpserver used by ktt.lib.httpserver

    Authenticator
    Before each request is processed, the authenticator determines whether to cancel the request or now.
    ExchangePacket
    This class is a simplified implementation of HttpExchange.

    HttpServer
    This class is a simplified implementation of HttpServer.
    At least one RequestHandler must be created in order to process requests.

    This class is a simplified implementation of HttpHandler.
    A handler used to process HTTP exchanges.
